video.title: Wynonna Earp
video.synopsis: The outcast descendant of lawman Wyatt Earp teams up with an immortal Doc Holliday to rid the world of demonic revenants from the Wild West.

episodes.synopsis: On her way home for her uncle’s funeral, rowdy Wynonna Earp finds herself sucked into the curse that has plagued her family for generations.
episodes.title: Purgatory

episodes.synopsis: While Doc attempts to ingratiate himself to them, the revenants set their sights on getting the Peacemaker out of Wynonna's hands.
episodes.title: Keep the Home Fires Burning

episodes.synopsis: Waverly closes in on Doc's secret, and Wynonna and Dolls race to thwart a ritual that could set the revenants loose on the world.
episodes.title: Leavin' on Your Mind

episodes.synopsis: A skeptical Wynonna forces Doc into a telling game of target practice. The team investigates a woman’s bizarre, mirror-related death.
episodes.title: The Blade

episodes.synopsis: Wynonna has a disturbing nightmare about Willa. Dolls leads a raid after seeing the revenants transport a conspicuous crate into the trailer park.
episodes.title: Digging Up Bones

episodes.synopsis: Dolls’s secret comes out when he joins Wynonna to find the mysterious Blacksmith and encounters a secluded family with a voracious appetite.
episodes.title: Constant Cravings

episodes.synopsis: Now the protector of the skull, Waverly decides to throw a party at the homestead. An angry 100-year-old witch quickly closes in on the Earp sisters.
episodes.title: Walkin' After Midnight

episodes.synopsis: As Waverly, Doc and Dolls close in on the last of the seven revenants they're after, Wynonna wakes to find herself the prisoner of a demented killer.
episodes.title: Two-Faced Jack

episodes.synopsis: Constance storms Bobo’s shed to retrieve her family’s bones. A newly recovered Wynonna faces a tough challenge from a Black Badge analyst.
episodes.title: Bury Me with My Guns On

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to track down an enemy of Bobo’s who may have answers, Dolls and Wynonna head to the Pine Barrens. But a cult there harbors a shocking secret.
episodes.title: She Wouldn't Be Gone

episodes.synopsis: The Earp sisters welcome their newest guest. Bobo prepares for the Poker Spectacular as two unlucky revenants revive a pair of sinister twins.
episodes.title: Landslide

episodes.synopsis: As Bobo continues his gruesome party planning, Dolls and Wynonna infiltrate a local gang’s clubhouse but run into problems with the Peacemaker.
episodes.title: House of Memories

episodes.synopsis: The Peacemaker goes missing. After Bobo places a bounty on Wynonna’s head, she faces a heartbreaking choice in her quest to take down the revenants.
episodes.title: I Walk the Line

episodes.synopsis: Dolls calls in a favor, but one might not be enough. Meanwhile, Wynonna rides to the rescue, and an unexpected new ally joins the fracas.
episodes.title: Steel Bars and Stone Walls

episodes.synopsis: Waverly's transformation shows no signs of slowing down, and Wynonna learns even the Peacemaker has its limits. Doc strikes a deal.
episodes.title: Shed Your Skin

episodes.synopsis: With homecoming on the horizon, Doc does his darndest to help out a friend while Wynonna sets her sights on a sinister symbol.
episodes.title: Gonna Getcha Good

episodes.synopsis: After a Black Badge agent is brutally beaten for his briefcase, Wynonna and her team pursue the attackers high and low.
episodes.title: She Ain't Right

episodes.synopsis: As a snowstorm looms, Wynonna's personality shift raises some eyebrows. Meanwhile, Jeremy learns not to judge a plate by its paint.
episodes.title: Let's Pretend We're Strangers

episodes.synopsis: Wynonna's deep discussion with Dolls is put on hold when the Widows put a sleeping spell on the town.
episodes.title: Whiskey Lullaby

episodes.synopsis: As a past mistake comes back to bite Wynonna, Doc finds himself with an unwelcome title that's both brand-new and as old as the hills.
episodes.title: Everybody Knows

episodes.synopsis: Waverly wrestles with her sense of identity. After disappearing, Wynonna leaves a few breadcrumbs for Dolls. Rosita volunteers to throw a baby shower.
episodes.title: No Future in the Past

episodes.synopsis: Wynonna lays an impossible choice on Doc. While trying to relax at a spa, Waverly bumps into an old acquaintance. Doc's ring draws some attention.
episodes.title: Forever Mine Nevermind

episodes.synopsis: A savage attack puts a key member of the group in mortal danger and leaves everyone else desperate for a way to help.
episodes.title: I See a Darkness

episodes.synopsis: As Wynonna and Doc try to make sense of their bizarre new realities, the Widows prepare to welcome back one of their own for a homecoming humdinger.
episodes.title: Gone as a Girl Can Get

episodes.synopsis: In the climactic battle, a very pregnant Wynonna joins her crew for a final face off against the Widows. It's not easy being an Earp.
episodes.title: I Hope You Dance

episodes.synopsis: When a busload of mesmerizing vampires scheme their way into town, Wynonna investigates their arrival to defend Purgatory from their charming trance.
episodes.title: Blood Red and Going Down

episodes.synopsis: The Earp sisters collide with a voice-stealing revenant, leaving Waverly as human fare and a Peacemaker-less Wynonna on the hunt for her sister.
episodes.title: When You Call My Name

episodes.synopsis: One of Dolls' Black Badge division colleagues arrives in Purgatory as the team deals with the aftermath of a devastating loss.
episodes.title: Colder Weather

episodes.synopsis: An alarming visit to see her mother leaves Wynonna, Waverly and gang in grave danger. Meanwhile, Jeremy and Robin uncover the forest's secrets.
episodes.title: No Cure for Crazy

episodes.synopsis: Armed with bewitching sweets and damaging truths, a beguiling she-demon drives wedges between the Earp sisters, Doc and Nicole.
episodes.title: Jolene

episodes.synopsis: While Wynonna joins forces with a new ally to search for a missing kid on Christmas Day, Waverly learns more about her father.
episodes.title: If We Make It Through December

episodes.synopsis: A spat between Wynonna and Nicole over supernatural artifacts releases a pesky spirit into Purgatory. Elsewhere, Doc adjusts to a new undead lifestyle.
episodes.title: I Fall to Pieces

episodes.synopsis: Doc's thirst for blood spoils Wynonna's date night while a former foe swipes tarot cards that expose a shocking connection to Bulshar.
episodes.title: Waiting Forever for You

episodes.synopsis: Trapped in a recurring Bulshar-induced nightmare, Wynonna is faced with an impossible choice between herself and a loved one.
episodes.title: Undo It

episodes.synopsis: As a mysterious woman helps the Earps beat Bulshar, Nicole and Doc encounter a deadly fire witch harboring the key to defeating the powerful demon.
episodes.title: The Other Woman

episodes.synopsis: With an apocalypse on the horizon, Wynonna forms an attack on Bulshar as Nicole evacuates Purgatory. Waverly is spooked by a loved one's resurrection.
episodes.title: Daddy Lessons

episodes.synopsis: Wynonna and Waverly engage in a final attempt to end the family curse and kill Bulshar before the Earp line ceases to exist.
episodes.title: War Paint

episodes.synopsis: Wynonna and Nedley gear up and set off in search of their lost friends. Meanwhile, Nicole wakes up on a train rapidly heading away from Purgatory.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Zombies cut Wynnona and Nicole's happy reunion short. Waverly and Doc also reunite with a loved one, but something feels off.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Chrissy Nedley places Wynonna under arrest. While attempting to exonerate her, Doc runs into a monster who might not be an enemy.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Wynonna reunites with an old colleague and meets an ancient enemy. Nicole and Waverly search for Peacemaker, and Rachel crushes on a boy with a secret.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: The homestead catches fire while Team Earp is sleeping, pushing them to kick the search for Peacemaker into high gear. Meanwhile, Nicole falls ill.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Nicole undergoes an exorcism and Wynonna fights an old enemy. As the gang faces off against the Clantons, their relationships are tested.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Nicole and Waverly celebrate their engagement and Doc avoids Wynonna as mysterious pink specks infect the town of Purgatory with love sickness.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: On Halloween, a demonic scarecrow terrorizes Purgatory. Waverly and Wynonna chase after him, but the sisters are in for a night they'll never forget.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: The gang tries to convince Nicole to become sheriff again. Meanwhile, trivia night gets messy when someone starts stealing the winners' brains.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Waverly and Nicole stage an intervention for Wynonna's drinking and demon-killing spree, but their hesitations must wait when a deadly foe reappears.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: After Waverly's big change, the gang and their enemies undergo a series of life-altering transformations of their own.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: On Nicole and Waverly's wedding day, Team Earp must battle a malevolent witch. Wynonna learns that Doc is leaving Purgatory for good.
episodes.title: Episode 12
